{"type":"message","id":"abc3a13d","parentId":"718f5af3","timestamp":"2026-03-28T01:32:05.413Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_G9W0fqV24avw5Fs4QkpBoZTL","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"== signal help ==\nGet latest signal list (smart money / KOL / whale activity)\n\nUsage: onchainos signal list [OPTIONS] --chain <CHAIN>\n\nOptions:\n      --base-url <BASE_URL>\n          Backend service URL (overrides config)\n      --chain <CHAIN>\n          Chain (e.g. ethereum, solana, base). Required\n      --wallet-type <WALLET_TYPE>\n          Wallet type filter: 1=Smart Money, 2=KOL/Influencer, 3=Whales (comma-separated, e.g. \"1,2\")\n      --min-amount-usd <MIN_AMOUNT_USD>\n          Minimum transaction amount in USD\n      --max-amount-usd <MAX_AMOUNT_USD>\n          Maximum transaction amount in USD\n      --min-address-count <MIN_ADDRESS_COUNT>\n          Minimum triggering wallet address count\n      --max-address-count <MAX_ADDRESS_COUNT>\n          Maximum triggering wallet address count\n      --token-address <TOKEN_ADDRESS>\n          Token contract address (filter signals for a specific token)\n      --min-market-cap-usd <MIN_MARKET_CAP_USD>\n          Minimum token market cap in USD\n      --max-market-cap-usd <MAX_MARKET_CAP_USD>\n          Maximum token market cap in USD\n      --min-liquidity-usd <MIN_LIQUIDITY_USD>\n          Minimum token liquidity in USD\n      --max-liquidity-usd <MAX_LIQUIDITY_USD>\n          Maximum token liquidity in USD\n  -h, --help\n          Print help\n\n== token hot-tokens help ==\nGet hot token list ranked by trending score or X mentions (max 100 results)\n\nUsage: onchainos token hot-tokens [OPTIONS]\n\nOptions:\n      --base-url <BASE_URL>\n          Backend service URL (overrides config)\n      --ranking-type <RANKING_TYPE>\n          Ranking type: 4=Trending (token score), 5=Xmentioned (Twitter mentions) [default: 4]\n      --chain <CHAIN>\n          Chain filter (e.g. ethereum, solana). Default: all chains\n      --rank-by <RANK_BY>\n          Sort field: 1=price, 2=price change, 3=txs, 4=unique traders, 5=volume, 6=market cap, 7=liquidity, 8=created time, 9=OKX search count, 10=holders, 11=mention count, 12=social score, 14=net inflow, 15=token score\n      --time-frame <TIME_FRAME>\n          Time frame: 1=5min, 2=1h, 3=4h, 4=24h\n      --risk-filter <RISK_FILTER>\n          Hide risky tokens (true/false, default: true)\n      --stable-token-filter <STABLE_TOKEN_FILTER>\n          Filter stable coins (true/false, default: true)\n      --project-id <PROJECT_ID>\n          Protocol ID filter, comma-separated (e.g. 120596 for Pump.fun)\n      --price-change-min <PRICE_CHANGE_MIN>\n          Min price change percent (can be negative, e.g. -5)\n      --price-change-max <PRICE_CHANGE_MAX>\n          Max price change percent (can be negative, e.g. -5 for losers)\n      --volume-min <VOLUME_MIN>\n          Min volume (USD)\n      --volume-max <VOLUME_MAX>\n          Max volume (USD)\n      --market-cap-min <MARKET_CAP_MIN>\n          Min market cap (USD)\n      --market-cap-max <MARKET_CAP_MAX>\n          Max market cap (USD)\n      --liquidity-min <LIQUIDITY_MIN>\n          Min liquidity (USD)\n      --liquidity-max <LIQUIDITY_MAX>\n          Max liquidity (USD)\n      --transaction-min <TRANSACTION_MIN>\n          Min transaction count (tradeAmount)\n      --transaction-max <TRANSACTION_MAX>\n          Max transaction count (tradeAmount)\n      --txs-min <TXS_MIN>\n          Min txs count\n      --txs-max <TXS_MAX>\n          Max txs count\n      --unique-trader-min <UNIQUE_TRADER_MIN>\n          Min unique traders\n      --unique-trader-max <UNIQUE_TRADER_MAX>\n          Max unique traders\n      --holders-min <HOLDERS_MIN>\n          Min holders\n      --holders-max <HOLDERS_MAX>\n          Max holders\n      --inflow-min <INFLOW_MIN>\n          Min net inflow USD\n      --inflow-max <INFLOW_MAX>\n          Max net inflow USD\n      --fdv-min <FDV_MIN>\n          Min FDV (USD)\n      --fdv-max <FDV_MAX>\n          Max FDV (USD)\n      --mentioned-count-min <MENTIONED_COUNT_MIN>\n          Min mention count (for Xmentioned ranking)\n      --mentioned-count-max <MENTIONED_COUNT_MAX>\n          Max mention count\n      --social-score-min <SOCIAL_SCORE_MIN>\n          Min social score\n      --social-score-max <SOCIAL_SCORE_MAX>\n          Max social score\n      --top10-hold-percent-min <TOP10_HOLD_PERCENT_MIN>\n          Min top-10 holder percent\n      --top10-hold-percent-max <TOP10_HOLD_PERCENT_MAX>\n          Max top-10 holder percent\n      --dev-hold-percent-min <DEV_HOLD_PERCENT_MIN>\n          Min dev hold percent\n      --dev-hold-percent-max <DEV_HOLD_PERCENT_MAX>\n          Max dev hold percent\n      --bundle-hold-percent-min <BUNDLE_HOLD_PERCENT_MIN>\n          Min bundle hold percent\n      --bundle-hold-percent-max <BUNDLE_HOLD_PERCENT_MAX>\n          Max bundle hold percent\n      --suspicious-hold-percent-min <SUSPICIOUS_HOLD_PERCENT_MIN>\n          Min suspicious hold percent\n      --suspicious-hold-percent-max <SUSPICIOUS_HOLD_PERCENT_MAX>\n          Max suspicious hold percent\n      --is-lp-burnt <IS_LP_BURNT>\n          LP burned filter (true/false, default: true)\n      --is-mint <IS_MINT>\n          Mintable filter (true/false, default: true)\n      --is-freeze <IS_FREEZE>\n          Freeze filter (true/false, default: true)\n  -h, --help\n          Print help\n\n== token search DOGE ==\n{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"chainIndex\": \"1\",\n      \"change\": \"-1.64\",\n      \"cursor\": \"0\",\n      \"decimal\": \"8\",\n      \"explorerUrl\": \"https://web3.okx.com/explorer/ethereum/token/0x4206931337dc273a630d328da6441786bfad668f\",\n      \"holders\": \"4775\",\n      \"liquidity\": \"5727516.49400889631159077659095066\",\n      \"marketCap\": \"4969002.519855073231447851\",\n      \"price\": \"0.090242407903197164\",\n      \"tagList\": {\n        \"communityRecogniz